* Channel Switching Simulation: 16 channels multiplexed
* Op-amp: LMC6001 Ultra-Low Bias, Range 8: Rf=10G
* Each channel has different DC current (halving pattern)
* Channels switch every 200ms

* ---- Power Supply ----
VCC VCC 0 DC 5
VEE VEE 0 DC -5

* ---- Mux Switch Model ----
.model SW_MUX SW(VT=2.5 VH=0.5 RON=100 ROFF=1e12)

* ---- Channel 1: I=100.0fA ----
* Sensor model: current source with R_DUT ground return
Isrc1 0 CH1_IN DC 1e-13
R_DUT1 CH1_IN 0 100Meg
R_IN1 CH1_IN MUX1_IN 1k
S_MUX1 MUX1_IN TIA_IN EN1 0 SW_MUX
* ---- Channel 2: I=250.0fA ----
